snippet: The government announced it was giving people two more days to sign up for 2016 health coverage through the federal marketplace. Enrollment was to have ended Tuesday night.
lead_paragraph: The government announced it was giving people two more days to sign up for 2016 health coverage through the federal marketplace. Enrollment was to have ended Tuesday night.
